{"tid":2449829,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"玩家改善《GTA Online》讀取過慢問題 R星致贈1萬美金並承諾更新","createTime":"2021-03-17T03:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T15:27:59.000Z","uid":250308,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"db59cba054097cdb7fddf74fd89114df66cf0c95","tid":2449829,"uid":250308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:27:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pcgamer.com/rockstar-thanks-gta-online-player-who-fixed-poor-load-times-official-update-coming/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcgamer.com%2Frockstar-thanks-gta-online-player-who-fixed-poor-load-times-official-update-coming%2F&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixawvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=9300edd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcgamer.com/rockstar-thanks-gta-online-player-who-fixed-poor-load-times-official-update-coming/</a><br />\n之前遊戲角落曾報導，一名玩家成功解決了一直以來《俠盜獵車手 Online》（GTA Online）讀取過久的問題，在網路披露解方後，居然正式受到了官方的關注，將在未來更新中使用這名玩家的方案，並奉上獎金感謝這名玩家。<br />\n<br />\n《俠盜獵車手 Online》在線上模式推出的7年間更新了許多精彩的跟活動跟內容，唯獨讀取時間仍遭人詬病至今。就在上月底， 一名暱稱「T0st」（tostercx）的玩家在PC平台上的測試，成功地將讀取時間縮短了70%。他也將修復方式放在個人網站與Github上。<br />\n<br />\n就在今日，Rockstar Games官方向外媒PC Gamer證實，經過內部調查，T0st的方法的確改善了遊戲的讀取，已經著手修正，將在下一次改版實裝。不過Rockstar沒有說明是否如T0st所說的，減少了70％的讀取時間。<br />\n<br />\nRockstar事後也聯繫T0st，並贈送了一萬美金的獎金作為報酬。這筆獎金通常作為Rockstar線上遊戲中安全性漏洞回報計畫（Bug Bounty program）的獎勵，不過官方表示這次將作為特例感謝這名玩家。"},{"pid":"f934b20fdba46673391d97891910f8bbe0fce486","tid":2449829,"uid":158499,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:28:15.000Z","msg":"應該請佢啦，咁大個團隊冇人夠佢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bad9c067bf4db6b1c33534c67881393f3abe7e","tid":2449829,"uid":356010,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"黑客也打機"},{"pid":"beb4b3feb7a359314b884666bb138d5334c0bf23","tid":2449829,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:39:23.000Z","msg":"減得30%都夠<br />\nr 星專家食屎.jpg"}